OL,3,CAmbulance service suspends X account
OL,4,Camid 'hate speech and misinformation'
OL,6,FAn ambulance service has suspended its
OL,7,Faccount on the social media site X due
OL,8,Fto what it has described as a "sharp
OL,9,Frise in hate speech and
OL,10,Fmisinformation".
OL,12,FThe North East Ambulance Service said
OL,13,Fcontent on the platform, formerly
OL,14,Fknown as Twitter, is "not consistent
OL,15,Fwith its values".
OL,17,FIt will continue to post on other
OL,18,Fsocial media sites, including
OL,19,FFacebook, Instagram and LinkedIn.
