OL,6,FMark Cotton, assistant director of
OL,7,Fcommunications and engagement at North
OL,8,FEast Ambulance Service, said: "We have
OL,9,Ftaken the decision to suspend all our
OL,10,Fcorporate accounts on X.
OL,12,F"We feel strongly that the failure to
OL,13,Fpolice content on X allows the
OL,14,Fperpetuation of unacceptable and
OL,15,Foffensive content, which has seen a
OL,16,Fsharp rise in hate speech and
OL,17,Fmisinformation that is not consistent
OL,18,Fwith our values.
