OL,6,F"We expect our staff to uphold our
OL,7,Fvalues and standards when representing
OL,8,Four service and equally we should
OL,9,Fuphold those same values and standards
OL,10,Fwhen using social media.
OL,12,F"Social media platforms can be
OL,13,Fcontentious, but we will continue to
OL,14,Fuse Facebook, Instagram and LinkedIn
OL,15,Fwhere we have a large following which
OL,16,Fis growing, and we will seek
OL,17,Falternatives to X.
