OL,9,Fwelcoming and rewarding organisation."
OL,11,FThe ambulance service announced the
OL,12,Fclosure of its account on X with a
OL,13,Fpost on the site, which said: "We have
OL,14,Fsuspended this account because the X
OL,15,Fplatform is no longer consistent with
OL,16,Four values as an NHS emergency service.
OL,18,F"You can continue to follow North East
OL,19,FAmbulance Service on Facebook,
OL,20,FInstagram and LinkedIn."
